headline.print_headline: It's Jeter's Last, Puig's First All-Star Game
headline.main: It's Jeter's Last, Puig's First All-Star Game

lead_paragraph: Derek Jeter will be making his 14th and final All-Star appearance, while dynamic Yasiel Puig makes his Midsummer Classic debut on Tuesday in the contest where home field advantage in the World Series goes to the winning league.
